✅ 1. Classify each ticket by urgency based on priority
•	Priority 3 → 'High'
•	Priority 2 → 'Medium'
•	Priority 1 → 'Low'
ANS:
select * ,case
    -> when priority=3 then 'High'
    -> when priority=2 then 'Medium'
    -> else 'low'
    -> end as level_of_Urgency
    -> from tickets;
