✅ 5. Show ticket summary: "High Priority Open", "Low Priority Closed", or "Other"
ANS:
 select *, case
    ->     when priority=3 or priority=1
    ->     then case
    ->     when priority=3 and status='Open' then 'High priority and Open'
    ->     when priority=1 and status='Closed' then 'Low priority and Closed'
    ->     else 'Others'
    ->     end
    ->     else 'Others'
    ->     end as ticket_summary
    ->     from tickets;
+-----------+---------------+------------+----------+-----------+--------------+---------------+---------------+-------------------------+
| ticket_id | customer_name | issue_type | priority | status    | created_date | assigned_team | location      | ticket_summary          |
