✅ 19. Show only 'Software' tickets with extra labels: 'High Risk', 'Normal', etc.
ANS:
select *,case
    -> when priority=3 then 'High risk'
    -> when priority=2 then 'medium risk'
    -> else 'Normal'
    -> end as new_column
    -> from tickets where issue_type='Software';
+-----------+---------------+------------+----------+---------+--------------+---------------+---------------+-------------+
| ticket_id | customer_name | issue_type | priority | status  | created_date | assigned_team | location      | new_column  |
